 <datafield tag="999" ind1="C" ind2="5">
  <subfield code="o">10</subfield>
  <subfield code="m">The reality of {{ \Gamma }_{\sigma}} for conformal boundary states can be seen as a consequence of locality of the boundary condition</subfield>
